=== Alternatives ===
* '''Epson Scanners''': Looked at Epson WorkForce Pro DS-510 Workforce Document Scanner, but it doesn't appear officially supported by Epson on Linux (3rd party software is available for ~$100).
* '''Canon Scanners''': Way too expensive.
* '''Fujitsu ScanSnap iX500''': Replacement for the 1500. There is limited support by SANE, but Fujitsu contributes nothing to SANE. There is complete support for the old ScanSnap S1500 by SANE, but a used S1500 is very expensive.

